"     </a>",
"     <br/>",
"     <a class=\"medical medical_review\" href=\"UTD.htm?37/53/38745?source=see_link\">",
"      Use of psychotropic medications in breastfeeding women",
"     </a>",
"     <br/>",
"     <br/>",
"     The following organizations also provide reliable health information.",
"    </p>",
